He didn't even make an effort
in hitting Sima's return.

31
00:02:33,720 --> 00:02:35,360
The game has just begun.

32
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:38,360
He has already won the first round
just by serving.

33
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,720
[panting]
I'm exhausted.

34
00:02:40,800 --> 00:02:45,160
I never thought being a cheerleader
would be harder than playing tennis.

35
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,200
You tell me.

36
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:51,920
Wait.

37
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:52,880
[both] Thank you.

38
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:53,840
You are welcome.

39
