[Mu] It's bitter.

40
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:00,160
Do you want some?

41
00:03:01,040 --> 00:03:02,880
Uh, no. Thank you.

42
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,520
-Thank you.
-[Tang Jiale] Lu Xia.

43
00:03:04,600 --> 00:03:05,480
Well done.

44
00:03:06,040 --> 00:03:07,400
He is lucky

45
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,960
to be in a good environment

46
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,600
and have some great seniors.

47
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,480
I almost feel sorry for beating him.

48
00:03:13,560 --> 00:03:15,600
Lu Xia, don't look down on your opponent.

49
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:17,920
We can't underestimate
the strength of Yu Feng.

50
00:03:18,000 --> 00:03:18,960
[Tang Jiale] Mm-hm.

51
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,800
I am a good father.

52
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:23,880
Yes.

53
00:03:23,960 --> 00:03:25,320
And I am a good uncle.

54
00:03:29,480 --> 00:03:31,280
Lu Xia is in trouble this time.

55
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:33,360
[Yu Qing students] Go, Yu Qing!

56
00:03:33,440 --> 00:03:35,440
Why do you always say that?

57
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,000
[Yu Qing students] Go, Yu Qing!

58
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:38,360
Look at his face.

59
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:42,320
[Huang Jing] He won't give Lu Xia
a chance like I did.

60
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:44,760
Even Yan was beaten by Lu Xia.

61
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:48,920
I think he has a chance to win.
[chuckles]

62
00:03:56,440 --> 00:03:57,520
[tennis ball thumps]

63
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,920
[tense music]

64
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:10,320
I will give you
a taste of your own medicine.

65
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,800
[thwacks]

66
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,720
[ball whooshing]

67
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,800
Is that a Twist Serve?

68
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:31,800
The spinning and strength can't compare
with Lu Xia's.

69
00:04:31,880 --> 00:04:33,320
But it's hard to say.

70
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:37,320
I never thought we would meet players
with such serves at the regionals.

71
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,800
Everyone can do a Twist Serve.

72
00:04:41,240 --> 00:04:42,400
I can practice it too.

73
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:43,880
[Xiuwen gasps]

74
00:04:54,440 --> 00:04:56,040
You haven't shown it all, right?

75
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:58,680
This feels weird.

76
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:01,120
What is Yiwu talking about?

77
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:06,080
Does this freshman have other techniques?

78
00:05:13,160 --> 00:05:14,480
-[thwacks]
-[Yiwu grunts]

79
00:05:22,760 --> 00:05:24,240
What a nice lob.

80
00:05:32,440 --> 00:05:33,440
[pants, grunts]

81
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:36,000
[crowd cheering]

82
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,080
[sighs]

83
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,200
[laughs]

84
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:44,800
[Xing Zi] He has very good judgment.

85
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,520
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

86
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:52,760
SIMA YIWU VERSUS LU XIA, 0-2

87
00:05:52,840 --> 00:05:55,000
SIMA YIWU VERSUS LU XIA, 0-3

88
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,520
What are you waiting for?

89
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:01,440
[Ziping] You like making your opponents
feel elated at first,

90
00:06:01,520 --> 00:06:03,040
and then you crush them.

91
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:06,960
-But if you don't fight back now,
-[Yiwu grunts]

92
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,080
you may really lose this game.

93
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:11,960
[Yiwu grunts]

94
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,440
[umpire] That's 4-0.
Yu Qing is in the lead.

95
00:06:14,520 --> 00:06:16,640
[crowd cheering]

96
00:06:19,960 --> 00:06:22,360
Lu Xia has improved a lot.

97
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:26,080
Yes. We cannot treat him lightly.

98
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:30,320
[panting]

99
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:32,800
Even Yiwu is overpowered.

100
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:36,840
Who the hell is this freshman?

101
00:06:39,840 --> 00:06:41,720
[sighs]
The game has just begun.

102
00:06:42,960 --> 00:06:45,040
-[thwacking]
-[grunting]

103
00:06:46,400 --> 00:06:48,240
-[thwacking]
-[ball whooshing]

104
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:51,720
Yu Feng's attacks are a little strange.

105
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:55,920
It seems that he's only doing
Top Spin and Down Spin.

106
00:06:58,120 --> 00:06:59,080
Kid.

107
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,640
National games are tough, right?

108
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:05,960
[Lu Xia pants]

109
00:07:06,200 --> 00:07:08,320
[ball whooshing]

110
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,480
-[ball thumps]
-[Lu Xia grunts]

111
00:07:12,120 --> 00:07:13,280
[Lu Xia gasps]

112
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,840
[umpire] That's 0-15. Yu Feng scores.

113
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,320
What's going on?

114
00:07:20,760 --> 00:07:24,360
Lu Xia's movement seems a little weird.

115
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,720
What's their strategy?

116
00:07:26,280 --> 00:07:27,920
Will they reverse the game?

117
00:07:34,840 --> 00:07:36,280
[Yiwu] So many people care about you.

118
00:07:37,800 --> 00:07:39,840
I don't want you to have a bad day either.

119
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:43,240
[sighs]

120
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:48,440
[tense music]

121
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:54,400
[Ziping] The freshman just had a pause.

122
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:56,640
Top Spin and Down Spin.

123
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:59,160
You made it, Yiwu.

124
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:01,320
[Qiao Chen] Temporarily paralyzed?

125
00:08:01,400 --> 00:08:02,320
Yes.

126
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:05,880
He has to deal with the continuous
Top Spin and Down Spin.

127
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:08,400
[Xiangqian] It caused muscle contraction.

128
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:11,400
-[Lu Xia grunts, whimpers]
-Then he was temporarily paralyzed.

129
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:14,440
It won't last long, but...

130
00:08:14,760 --> 00:08:16,680
He is so cunning.

131
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:22,440
-[thwacking]
-[ball whooshing]

132
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:23,520
[Lu Xia grunts]

133
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:24,640
-[ball thwacks]
-[grunts]

134
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:25,840
[pants]

135
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:28,240
[Ziping] Even though his muscles
have contracted,

136
00:08:28,320 --> 00:08:30,640
he can still hit the ball

137
00:08:30,720 --> 00:08:32,240
and push Yiwu so hard.

138
00:08:34,799 --> 00:08:36,400
[Qiao Chen] Is it just me?

139
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:39,240
Do you think he's struggling
more and more?

140
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:41,320
Is his arm paralyzed?

141
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:45,799
Hey. Why aren't you worried?

142
00:08:47,799 --> 00:08:49,000
Take this.

143
00:08:58,640 --> 00:08:59,760
What are you doing?

144
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:01,960
I'm leaving.

145
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,640
I don't want to cause a commotion.

146
00:09:04,400 --> 00:09:06,200
Don't you care about Lu Xia?

147
00:09:06,560 --> 00:09:08,600
I believe that he can find a way.

148
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,200
I'm leaving.

149
00:09:10,280 --> 00:09:13,400
YU QING WILL WIN

150
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:16,600
[sighs]

151
00:09:16,880 --> 00:09:18,040
[camera shutter clicks]

152
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:28,160
[gasps]
What?

153
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:29,920
Where's the autographed photo?

154
00:09:31,360 --> 00:09:33,760
Lu Xiangqian?

155
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:35,840
Huh? You recognized me?

156
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:37,400
It's written on your head.

157
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,360
Fine, fine, fine.

158
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:42,120
You promised to give me
Hua Chenyu's autographed photo.

159
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:44,560
[Xiangqian] I even got a photo frame.

160
00:09:44,640 --> 00:09:45,880
You just disappeared.

161
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,880
I will give it to you
in your next interview.

162
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,760
I'm here to interview Lu Xia.

163
00:09:51,160 --> 00:09:52,800
-Lu Xia is my son.
-[camera shutter clicks]

164
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,520
Don't you need to ask for my permission?

165
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,520
Uh... next time.

166
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:59,560
Please don't disturb me while I'm working.

167
00:09:59,960 --> 00:10:00,800
You...

168
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:03,160
[camera shutter clicking]

169
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:04,400
-Stop, stop, stop.
-[chuckles]

170
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,240
You promised. Next time. I'm leaving.

171
00:10:06,320 --> 00:10:08,560
-You're not watching?
-[Xiangqian] The kid will find a way.

172
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,800
-[camera shutter clicking]
-[grunting]

173
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:16,040
TEMPORARY PARALYSIS

174
00:10:17,080 --> 00:10:18,120
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

175
00:10:19,520 --> 00:10:22,120
He is trying to hit the ball
by turning his body.

176
00:10:23,280 --> 00:10:25,000
[Lu Xia] What's wrong with my hand?

177
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,960
[tennis racket clatters]

178
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,680
[all gasp]

179
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:36,840
[student 1] Is he injured?

180
00:10:36,920 --> 00:10:39,200
-What should we do?
-[student 2] Is it serious?

181
00:10:39,320 --> 00:10:41,600
-It's dangerous.
-[Qiao Chen] Lu Xia.

182
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,480
[Tang Jiale gasps]

183
00:10:44,880 --> 00:10:46,880
[foreboding music]

184
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,400
[Lu Xia whimpers]

185
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,520
[Lu Xia] Don't enter the court.

186
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,880
[student 3] Is he okay?

187
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:03,560
-[student 4] Injured?
-[student 3] His eye is wounded.

188
00:11:04,920 --> 00:11:06,400
-[Peng] Ying.
-[man 1] You can't go in.

189
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,480
[Ying panting]

190
00:11:10,280 --> 00:11:11,480
Are you okay?

191
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,640
I didn't mean to.

192
00:11:15,040 --> 00:11:16,640
[Yiwu] It is just paralysis, right?

193
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:18,880
I didn't mean to.

194
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,800
What does that have to do with me?

195
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,800
[umpire] Time-out.

196
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:26,040
-Is it going to affect the game?
-He can't walk properly.

197
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,040
He needs help to walk.

198
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,400
-Look.
-It looks bad.

199
00:11:30,120 --> 00:11:31,480
Will he be blind?

200
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:34,160
[Yiwu] I finally met a tricky opponent.

201
00:11:34,760 --> 00:11:36,360
I won't deserve to win

202
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,680
if he is blind.

203
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:42,560
[sighs]

204
00:11:49,520 --> 00:11:51,520
[somber music]

205
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,920
[sighs]

206
00:11:59,080 --> 00:12:01,320
You are so impatient.
The doctor wasn't done yet.

207
00:12:01,680 --> 00:12:04,320
This is our last chance
to prepare for the nationals.

208
00:12:04,800 --> 00:12:06,560
We must celebrate victory with everyone.

209
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:12,080
-[doctor 1] Let me do that.
-[Qiao Chen] Is it serious?

210
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,880
[both gasp]

211
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,120
Doctor.

212
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,000
[Siyang] How is he now?

213
00:12:31,520 --> 00:12:32,840
[doctor 1] No eye damage.

214
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:35,320
-There's a deep cut on his eyelid.
-Are you okay?

215
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:37,520
You can't go on playing.

216
00:12:38,040 --> 00:12:39,080
How could this be?

217
00:12:41,520 --> 00:12:44,200
Please bring my spare racket.

218
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:45,840
Okay.

219
00:12:46,400 --> 00:12:49,160
Stop it. Look at yourself.

220
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:51,120
Don't force yourself.

221
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,440
You are at a disadvantage.

222
00:12:53,880 --> 00:12:54,720
[Coach Qi] What?

223
00:12:54,840 --> 00:12:56,400
You still want to play?

224
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:57,600
[Tang Jiale] Lu Xia.

225
00:12:57,680 --> 00:12:59,640
I know you'll regret it
if you give up now.

226
00:12:59,960 --> 00:13:02,880
But right now,
you have to listen to others.

227
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:06,200
-I'm okay.
-"Okay"?

228
00:13:06,280 --> 00:13:08,120
We just stopped the bleeding temporarily.

229
00:13:08,200 --> 00:13:10,200
[Coach Qi] I think you should go
to the hospital.

230
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:11,320
I can continue playing.

231
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,320
[Siyang] Lu Xia.

232
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:18,160
You have only ten minutes.

233
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:23,520
If the game doesn't end in ten minutes,
you have to give it up.

234
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,680
Understand?

235
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:26,040
[Lu Xia] Fine.

236
00:13:37,960 --> 00:13:39,440
[umpire] The game continues.

237
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:43,920
Coach.

238
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,920
Why don't you convince him to quit?

239
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:49,080
Look at them.

240
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:53,920
[Coach Qi] That's the meaning
of playing tennis.

241
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:57,240
These boys will not give up

242
00:13:57,920 --> 00:13:59,240
even a single game.

243
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,720
[somber music]

244
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,960
Captain, what is it?

245
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:17,640
Nothing, nothing.

246
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:19,080
Continue playing.

247
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:25,960
Lu Xia will never fall here.

248
00:14:26,440 --> 00:14:27,600
Mm-hm.

249
00:14:27,960 --> 00:14:31,880
[Yu Qing students] Come on, Lu Xia.
Come on, Lu Xia.

250
00:14:31,960 --> 00:14:34,480
Come on, Lu Xia. Come on, Lu Xia.

251
00:14:34,560 --> 00:14:35,800
[Lu Xia] Let's be serious.

252
00:14:37,720 --> 00:14:39,160
He is changing to his left hand.

253
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:43,240
[Yiwu] You're left-handed?

254
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:45,200
It was just temporarily paralyzed.

255
00:14:45,680 --> 00:14:47,440
[scoffs]
You are so arrogant.

256
00:14:47,760 --> 00:14:49,640
I'll let you have a taste of failure.

257
00:14:49,720 --> 00:14:50,840
I'm sorry,

258
00:14:50,920 --> 00:14:54,360
I don't want to lose
before winning the national championship.

259
00:14:54,800 --> 00:14:57,160
[Yiwu] Come. I haven't given my best yet.

260
00:14:57,480 --> 00:14:59,440
-[thwacking]
-[grunting]

261
00:15:03,360 --> 00:15:04,200
[gasps]

262
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:05,320
Huh?

263
00:15:05,400 --> 00:15:07,080
[all gasp]

264
00:15:07,160 --> 00:15:08,680
-What a pity.
-The ball was so close.

265
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,560
[He Xinglong] He has only one eye.

266
00:15:10,640 --> 00:15:13,400
He cannot tell the distance.

267
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,440
He will get used to it.

268
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:18,120
But most importantly, his paralyzed hand.

269
00:15:18,680 --> 00:15:19,920
We can't just sit here.

270
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:22,000
Let's cheer for him.

271
00:15:22,600 --> 00:15:26,600
[all] Come on, Lu Xia. Come on, Lu Xia.

272
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:29,360
-[thwacking]
-[grunting]

273
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:42,680
His arm is temporarily paralyzed,

274
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,760
then the power of his grip has decreased.

275
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:47,280
Even if he can tell the distance,

276
00:15:47,840 --> 00:15:49,120
he's not able to get the ball.

277
00:15:49,720 --> 00:15:52,720
I never expected that Yu Feng High School
would have such a talented player.

278
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:54,400
[Coach Qi] He was ignored all the time.

279
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:58,120
Yiwu completely controlled
the timing of the paralysis.

280
00:15:58,360 --> 00:16:00,320
[chuckles]
He is extraordinary.

281
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:02,840
He is concentrating
on Lu Xia's left corner.

282
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:06,840
He shows no mercy at all.

283
00:16:08,840 --> 00:16:09,760
Siyang.

284
00:16:10,160 --> 00:16:12,640
Is it okay to let him play
through the injury?

285
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:15,200
I will take him out when the time is up.

286
00:16:15,280 --> 00:16:16,400
Win or lose.

287
00:16:17,000 --> 00:16:19,760
I think he won't easily give up.

288
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:22,200
[Yiwu] The temporary paralysis
should affect your hand again.

289
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:29,680
[Lu Xia] I must score on the next one.

290
00:16:30,440 --> 00:16:32,200
[umpire] It's 4-3, Yu Feng serves.

291
00:16:32,680 --> 00:16:34,920
It's good to get everyone's sympathy.

292
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,800
But just remember your own words.

293
00:16:37,120 --> 00:16:38,800
You must hold on to the end.

294
00:16:39,160 --> 00:16:40,960
-I don't want to pause again--
-Hey.

295
00:16:41,040 --> 00:16:42,720
Sorry to interrupt your monologue.

296
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,480
But can you serve soon?

297
00:16:44,840 --> 00:16:47,360
I don't know what to call your tricks.

298
00:16:47,760 --> 00:16:49,320
But I've found your weakness.

299
00:16:50,040 --> 00:16:52,200
I don't have much time.
I have to beat you soon.

300
00:16:53,920 --> 00:16:55,600
How can you still be so arrogant?

301
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:57,400
[ball thumps]

302
00:16:58,680 --> 00:16:59,880
What?

303
00:16:59,960 --> 00:17:02,640
Did he really figure out
how to deal with the temporary paralysis?

304
00:17:03,440 --> 00:17:05,160
Or was he just bluffing?

305
00:17:06,640 --> 00:17:07,760
[ball whooshes]

306
00:17:08,520 --> 00:17:10,240
-[thwacking]
-[grunting]

307
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:14,040
[Yiwu] He's changing hands.

308
00:17:15,400 --> 00:17:17,319
[Lu Xia] Have you ever seen
a double volley?

309
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:20,920
It's Lu Xiangqian‘s strategy.

310
00:17:21,000 --> 00:17:23,560
[Ziping] His reflex is unbelievable.

311
00:17:24,079 --> 00:17:26,000
He changes hands so easily.

312
00:17:31,880 --> 00:17:33,200
DOUBLE VOLLEY

313
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:36,080
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

314
00:17:38,680 --> 00:17:41,480
Why does he keep doing the Down Spin?

315
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:44,160
Don't you play well
using Top Spin and Down Spin?

316
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:45,360
Keep doing those.

317
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:49,680
He cannot do a Top Spin
if the ball comes right at him.

318
00:17:50,440 --> 00:17:53,080
So it's not because he doesn't want to,
he just can't.

319
00:17:53,160 --> 00:17:55,880
He found a way
to break the deadlock so soon.

320
00:18:02,320 --> 00:18:05,440
Did Lu Xia learn this strategy
from his father?

321
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:08,240
Yes, to be a real first-class player

322
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:10,760
is not only to get over the weak backhand,

323
00:18:10,840 --> 00:18:13,920
but also to get over the obstacles.

324
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:17,960
This was the spirit that made Lu Xiangqian
get his own strategy.

325
00:18:18,760 --> 00:18:24,800
It is not good for Lu Xia
to keep imitating his father.

326
00:18:26,520 --> 00:18:29,120
We have a tough captain.

327
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:31,840
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

328
00:18:34,840 --> 00:18:36,400
Come on, little guy.

329
00:18:36,960 --> 00:18:38,160
Come on, Lu Xia.

330
00:18:38,240 --> 00:18:39,520
There are only two minutes left.

331
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:45,240
[Lu Xia panting]

332
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:49,640
Yiwu, it's the critical moment.

333
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,320
Come on, Yiwu.

334
00:18:52,960 --> 00:18:54,360
[Tienan] It can't end like this.

335
00:18:57,520 --> 00:18:59,000
He's bleeding.

336
00:19:01,200 --> 00:19:04,320
[Ziping] He still plays so well
despite the injury.

337
00:19:05,400 --> 00:19:07,760
What an incredible freshman.

338
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,520
I will end this game soon.

339
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:16,240
Yiwu, win this one.

340
00:19:16,320 --> 00:19:17,400
We still have a chance.

341
00:19:17,720 --> 00:19:18,720
It's still early.

342
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:20,200
I will not let you win.

343
00:19:22,120 --> 00:19:24,120
[action music]

344
00:19:26,560 --> 00:19:27,800
There's only one minute left.

345
00:19:29,920 --> 00:19:34,680
[Yu Qing students] Come on, Yu Qing.
Come on, Yu Qing.

346
00:19:36,960 --> 00:19:38,360
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

347
00:19:38,440 --> 00:19:40,680
Great! Yiwu is not giving up.

348
00:19:40,800 --> 00:19:42,240
He predicted Lu Xia's path.

349
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:43,640
Only 30 seconds left.

350
00:19:49,320 --> 00:19:50,240
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

351
00:19:53,200 --> 00:19:54,760
BACKSPIN BALL

352
00:19:55,440 --> 00:19:56,560
[grunts]

353
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:01,960
[ball whooshing]

354
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:11,240
[Yiwu pants]

355
00:20:11,560 --> 00:20:13,560
[action music]

356
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:19,240
[Yiwu panting]

357
00:20:20,160 --> 00:20:21,560
That was a Backspin Ball.

358
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:24,680
[umpire] The game is over. Yu Qing won.

359
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:27,280
[crowd cheering]

360
00:20:27,360 --> 00:20:28,600
-Yeah!
-Yes!

361
00:20:28,680 --> 00:20:30,120
Right on time.

362
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:31,560
[both] Yes!

363
00:20:32,880 --> 00:20:35,320
He made it.

364
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:36,800
Yeah!
[laughs]

365
00:20:36,880 --> 00:20:38,560
[student 5] We won. We won. We won.

366
00:20:39,760 --> 00:20:41,080
[Xiuwen laughs]

367
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,720
[student 5] We won. We won. We won.

368
00:20:43,360 --> 00:20:45,560
[all cheering]

369
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:46,920
Yes!

370
00:20:48,840 --> 00:20:50,400
[student 5] Great.

371
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:52,440
[student 6] Awesome!

372
00:20:52,920 --> 00:20:54,120
[Peng] Yes!

373
00:20:54,520 --> 00:20:56,800
Awesome! Lu Xia.

374
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,480
[Ying] Lu Xia is such a wonderful player.

375
00:20:58,560 --> 00:21:00,040
[umpire] Players, shake your hands.

376
00:21:01,960 --> 00:21:04,960
[cheering]

377
00:21:07,520 --> 00:21:09,240
[Qiao Chen] What food
is good for the eyes?

378
00:21:09,320 --> 00:21:11,000
[He Xinglong] Luckily,
he stopped bleeding.

379
00:21:11,360 --> 00:21:12,440
[Zhuo Zhi] He will be fine.

380
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:14,400
[Tang Jiale] He will not go blind, right?

381
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:16,240
[Dayong] Lu Xia, hold on.

382
00:21:16,320 --> 00:21:17,520
[Lu Xia] It hurts.

383
00:21:18,320 --> 00:21:19,680
[Baiyang] Lu Xia, well done.

384
00:21:20,080 --> 00:21:22,200
[Siyang] I'll let him take
a break these next few days.

385
00:21:25,280 --> 00:21:26,800
Sorry to have injured your player.

386
00:21:28,000 --> 00:21:29,600
But we will not lose again.

387
00:21:30,160 --> 00:21:33,120
I hope we can meet at nationals.

388
00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:35,520
I look forward
to playing against you next time.

389
00:21:38,320 --> 00:21:39,480
[Qiao Chen] Lu Xia.

390
00:21:40,280 --> 00:21:41,760
Let's go to the hospital.

391
00:21:42,200 --> 00:21:44,600
[Lu Xia] What? Put me down!

392
00:21:45,480 --> 00:21:46,640
[Lu Xia grunts]

393
00:21:49,320 --> 00:21:51,160
-See you then.
-Mm-hm.

394
00:21:54,600 --> 00:21:55,640
[Yiwu] Captain.

395
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:57,600
I lost.

396
00:21:57,960 --> 00:22:02,160
[all] Sorry.

397
00:22:10,720 --> 00:22:12,040
It's hard in the beginning.

398
00:22:12,120 --> 00:22:13,600
There's a first time for all of us.

399
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:15,600
Don't be discouraged.

400
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:17,880
[Ziping] We can't lose next time.

401
00:22:18,800 --> 00:22:20,480
Although we lost this game,

402
00:22:20,880 --> 00:22:22,120
we are still qualified.

403
00:22:22,600 --> 00:22:24,920
We've achieved what we promised.

404
00:22:26,080 --> 00:22:28,000
It's a long way to nationals.

405
00:22:28,360 --> 00:22:29,720
We have to fight on our own.

406
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:30,800
[all] Yes!

407
00:22:31,440 --> 00:22:33,440
OUTPATIENT SERVICE

408
00:22:36,840 --> 00:22:38,720
[doctor 2] Why are you
high school students

409
00:22:38,800 --> 00:22:40,160
risking your lives for a game?

410
00:22:40,240 --> 00:22:42,600
I have seen many of you
get your eyes and arms hurt.

411
00:22:43,320 --> 00:22:46,120
Will this affect his eyes?

412
00:22:46,200 --> 00:22:47,320
It's nothing serious.

413
00:22:47,400 --> 00:22:49,120
It's just superficial
and a little bleeding.

414
00:22:49,200 --> 00:22:51,120
[doctor 2] He'll be fine
in two or three days.

415
00:22:51,880 --> 00:22:53,240
Kid, does it hurt?

416
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,600
Yes.

417
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,680
[comical music]

418
00:23:08,960 --> 00:23:11,520
His injury is nothing serious.

419
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:14,000
[Siyang] But remember,

420
00:23:14,080 --> 00:23:16,720
ensuring your own safety
is also important for the team.

421
00:23:17,760 --> 00:23:18,840
Got it?

422
00:23:18,920 --> 00:23:19,760
Got it.

423
00:23:19,840 --> 00:23:21,000
Fine.

424
00:23:21,080 --> 00:23:22,000
Let's go.

425
00:23:28,080 --> 00:23:30,080
[Sha panting]

426
00:23:34,400 --> 00:23:35,760
Where am I?

427
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:39,480
[sighs]

428
00:23:40,840 --> 00:23:42,960
Lu Xia bled for our team today.

429
00:23:43,040 --> 00:23:45,200
We’ll make it up to you
at the celebration.

430
00:23:45,280 --> 00:23:46,360
I'm not going.

431
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,680
Huh? You cannot escape.

432
00:23:48,920 --> 00:23:50,320
You must come.

433
00:23:50,520 --> 00:23:52,120
Our roasted goose is tasty.

434
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:54,520
I'll have my dad make you
some goose soup tonight.

435
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:56,600
Yes, the goose is the best.

436
00:23:56,680 --> 00:23:58,520
-Ying, come and have some, okay?
-Okay.

437
00:23:58,600 --> 00:24:00,320
[Sha sighs]
[Sha] Finally, I found you.

438
00:24:01,160 --> 00:24:02,400
How is your eye?

439
00:24:02,800 --> 00:24:04,440
Ah! He's fine.

440
00:24:04,520 --> 00:24:05,600
[Sha] Uh...

441
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,360
Now that I've met you, let's take a photo.

442
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,480
Fine. Come on.

443
00:24:09,560 --> 00:24:10,600
-Come on.
-[Sha] Come on.

444
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:15,760
Look here. Three, two, one.

445
00:24:15,840 --> 00:24:17,160
[camera shutter clicks]

446
00:24:19,320 --> 00:24:22,200
[Qiao Chen] Lu Xia,
you are the biggest hero today.

447
00:24:23,800 --> 00:24:26,280
Chi, Jiale, and Baiyang also won, right?

448
00:24:26,840 --> 00:24:28,160
Okay, boy.

449
00:24:28,560 --> 00:24:33,720
I am so grateful that you said that
and that you think that way.

450
00:24:35,200 --> 00:24:36,720
It's just a victory.

451
00:24:36,800 --> 00:24:37,960
Right.

452
00:24:38,080 --> 00:24:39,920
It is teamwork.

453
00:24:40,000 --> 00:24:41,240
We are all heroes.

454
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:42,480
Mm-hm.

455
00:24:42,920 --> 00:24:45,760
Here's a little secret.

456
00:24:48,400 --> 00:24:49,360
Ying.

457
00:24:49,520 --> 00:24:51,360
Who did you cheer for today?

458
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,640
I didn't.

459
00:24:57,320 --> 00:24:59,600
We don't need to point it out.

460
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:02,000
We all saw

461
00:25:02,080 --> 00:25:03,680
-who you were cheering for today.
-Mm-hm.

462
00:25:03,760 --> 00:25:05,040
Jiale, don't talk anymore.

463
00:25:05,280 --> 00:25:06,600
Then you talk more.

464
00:25:08,680 --> 00:25:10,320
Stop it.

465
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:12,920
You all did a good job today.

466
00:25:13,080 --> 00:25:15,560
Let's do our best

467
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:18,200
and achieve the final victory.

468
00:25:18,800 --> 00:25:19,680
Yu Qing!

469
00:25:19,800 --> 00:25:21,200
-Bound to win!
-Cheers.

470
00:25:21,280 --> 00:25:22,400
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

471
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:25,720
Here.

472
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:31,200
Lu Xia, what else would you like?

473
00:25:31,280 --> 00:25:33,880
My father cooks for our celebrations.

474
00:25:33,960 --> 00:25:35,680
Help yourselves.

475
00:25:35,760 --> 00:25:38,880
Yes, players can't win
on an empty stomach.

476
00:25:38,960 --> 00:25:41,000
[Mr. He] Help yourselves. There's more.

477
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:43,200
Xinglong, take care of them.

478
00:25:43,280 --> 00:25:44,280
Okay, Dad.

479
00:25:45,800 --> 00:25:47,120
[He Xinglong sighs]

480
00:25:51,720 --> 00:25:52,840
Excuse me.

481
00:25:55,440 --> 00:25:56,560
Okay.

482
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:58,440
You're all hungry, right?

483
00:25:59,160 --> 00:26:00,560
-Let's eat.
-[Tang Jiale] Yes.

484
00:26:02,440 --> 00:26:04,440
[somber music]

485
00:26:05,720 --> 00:26:09,040
[Mr. He groaning]

486
00:26:11,240 --> 00:26:12,920
-[Qiao Chen] Jiale, give me some goose.
-Hm?

487
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:13,840
Here.

488
00:26:15,680 --> 00:26:17,000
[Qiao Chen] Thanks.

489
00:26:17,160 --> 00:26:18,120
[laughs]

490
00:26:22,320 --> 00:26:25,280
You eat like a horse
even though you didn't play today.

491
00:26:27,120 --> 00:26:29,320
I saw Qiao Chen talking
with a girl from Yu Feng today,

492
00:26:29,400 --> 00:26:30,320
and they looked happy.

493
00:26:31,040 --> 00:26:32,440
Do you two know each other?

494
00:26:34,080 --> 00:26:35,360
Really?

495
00:26:36,360 --> 00:26:38,800
It's breaking news.

496
00:26:38,880 --> 00:26:40,760
Qiao Chen, who is that girl?

497
00:26:40,840 --> 00:26:42,560
What's your relationship?
How did you meet?

498
00:26:42,640 --> 00:26:43,720
Um...

499
00:26:43,800 --> 00:26:45,800
She is Xu Ziping's younger sister,

500
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:48,000
my middle school classmate.

501
00:26:48,320 --> 00:26:51,800
I often borrowed her money
for hamburgers back then.

502
00:26:52,360 --> 00:26:55,720
So we got to know each other
more and more.

503
00:26:55,800 --> 00:26:57,400
[Tang Jiale and Ying chuckle]

504
00:26:58,200 --> 00:27:00,840
You're killing my appetite.

505
00:27:01,400 --> 00:27:02,960
How can a boy be so sentimental?

506
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,520
[chuckles]

507
00:27:09,560 --> 00:27:10,640
[Tang Jiale] Hm?

508
00:27:10,760 --> 00:27:12,400
Zhuo Zhi, what sauce is this?

509
00:27:19,080 --> 00:27:20,240
Is it good?

510
00:27:22,280 --> 00:27:23,400
Oh!

511
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:25,440
[groans, coughs]

512
00:27:25,520 --> 00:27:26,600
[Tang Jiale] It's so spicy.

513
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:28,560
What is it?

514
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:30,760
My newly made spicy sauce.

515
00:27:30,840 --> 00:27:33,040
Xinglong! Bring me some water.

516
00:27:33,120 --> 00:27:34,040
It's so spicy.

517
00:27:34,120 --> 00:27:35,640
Just a minute.

518
00:27:36,200 --> 00:27:37,360
Who made this?

519
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:40,080
-Zhuo Zhi.
-Mm?

520
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:41,880
Please tell me your recipe.

521
00:27:41,960 --> 00:27:42,920
No.

522
00:27:43,360 --> 00:27:44,960
It is too spicy.

523
00:27:45,080 --> 00:27:46,160
[shushes]

524
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,120
Uh?

525
00:27:57,080 --> 00:27:59,800
[Tang Jiale and Ying gasp]

526
00:28:00,200 --> 00:28:02,200
[comical music]

527
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:06,120
[chuckles]

528
00:28:11,640 --> 00:28:12,680
[Zhuo Zhi chuckles]

529
00:28:17,200 --> 00:28:19,200
[Siyang] Okay, everyone.
Go home and have some rest.

530
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:20,840
We have practice tomorrow.

531
00:28:21,080 --> 00:28:22,000
Bye.

532
00:28:22,080 --> 00:28:23,000
[all] Bye.

533
00:28:23,080 --> 00:28:25,120
-Goodnight. Bye.
-Bye.

534
00:28:27,280 --> 00:28:28,240
Lu Xia.

535
00:28:31,360 --> 00:28:32,960
My aunt is coming to pick me up.

536
00:28:33,080 --> 00:28:34,560
Shall we go together?

537
00:28:34,640 --> 00:28:36,680
No, thanks. My house is near.

538
00:28:42,120 --> 00:28:44,120
[calm music]

539
